This configure come from https://github.com/mrcotter/mrcotter_dotfiles
and I did some modificaiton.

Before using these configure files, first install mpv by
brew install mpv --with-bundle
brew linkapps mpv

then put the mpv directory under ~/.config/mpv

more details refer to
http://bbs.feng.com/read-htm-tid-9633783.html
https://www.v2ex.com/t/157485
https://songchenwen.com/tech/2015/05/09/mpv-player/
